    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO SERIES - REMOVE - GEAR SHIFT LEVER</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="2">
        <title>GEAR SHIFT LEVER</title>
        <para>Remote control housings are removed the same way as gear shift levers.</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the four (4) retaining bolts from the gear shift lever base (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301714">Figure 14</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301714" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301714" filename="../figg13/G1301714.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 14. Gear Shift Lever Bolts</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">To break the gasket seal, lightly jar the gear shift housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301714">Figure 14</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the gear shift lever housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301715">Figure 15</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301715" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301715" filename="../figg13/G1301715.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 15. Remove Gasket</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the gasket and clean all mounting surfaces of gasket material (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301715">Figure 15</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
